{"tid":666992,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩SIM CARD / WIFI 蛋適合不斷飛既空姐/空少用？","createTime":"2018-05-16T10:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T13:27:40.000Z","uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5502b240ea88389934a12f4b654eb731df8dff4e","tid":666992,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"如題。市面上有好多產品提供短期無限數據，比人短期去旅行用（多數係10日內或者1個月內）。<br />\n<br />\n去exchange / working holiday 幾個月 / 一年既，就可能會喺當地買prepaid SIM / 當地上台等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但空姐、空少呢類，有機會飛世界唔同地方，但每次都只係短暫停留，有咩SIM CARD 或者WIFI 蛋會適合呢一類人？</strong><br />\n<br />\n之前我諗倒ONESIM，但睇Facebook 同埋佢地網頁，似乎係準備結束營業：<a href=\"https://www.onesim.asia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onesim.asia%2F&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3bdb0b56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.onesim.asia/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前我去exchange都用過ONESIM，因為會去唔同國家旅行，覺得係幾好用。同埋只係想睇map + whatsapp，去到住既地方 / 有WiFi既地方會用翻WiFi的話，ONESIM係一個好既選擇。而家冇左ONESIM既話，有咩產品會適合呢？"},{"pid":"eb0b0b72bc2ea32007981d1369b07e7ab982c728","tid":666992,"uid":183562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73629d4b6f07f6002ccc51a962b710a322402713","tid":666992,"uid":183550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e953b632d34551ab8f10520be1d9bc53a168a8f","tid":666992,"uid":175521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16b51de1e485995711598d471c7f9b05f9e05866","tid":666992,"uid":340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.birdie.com.hk/tbirdie/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.birdie.com.hk%2Ftbirdie%2Fzh&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a5056f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.birdie.com.hk/tbirdie/zh</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a8b218f09f816cdbf3a53c0e1674fa1e20c368","tid":666992,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b51de1e485995711598d471c7f9b05f9e05866","tid":666992,"uid":340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.birdie.com.hk/tbirdie/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.birdie.com.hk%2Ftbirdie%2Fzh&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a5056f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.birdie.com.hk/tbirdie/zh</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"好提議。亞洲地區我覺得Birdie ok，可惜美 / 歐 / 非既話就略貴<br />\n<br />\n參考：ONESIM 128kbps 無限<br />\nHKD368 / 14日<br />\nHKD468 / 30日<br />\n<br />\n通常長途機去倒歐 / 美都有機會stay翻40小時左右，Birdie 的話消費就已經高達 $80 - $120 ($40/d 或$60d計算)。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，唔知係咪各國電訊商覺得ONESIM出現令佢地漫遊既收入少左，所以而家整死左ONESIM"}]}